Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖 別哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們肯定會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這就結束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這個啊 誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經在某地 有位擁有神奇力量的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他所畫的畫就像有生命一般 能自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}人們都覺得毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和尚越來越難以跟別人相處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}於是他就孤身一人 安靜地躲在山中過日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:09.20,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I think of how it all was made
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我思考著這一切是如何被創造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:15.93,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Each detail of this world portrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}描寫了這世界每一個細節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:22.31,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In bursts of color, every sight and sound
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}連接出現的無數色彩 一切的景象和聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:29.28,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The wide blue sky and the immobile ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}還有廣闊的藍天與穩固的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:36.57,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all too great to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這一切偉大得讓人難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:43.07,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The moon, with one stroke of his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在他著下一筆後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:49.74,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Started to glow and all the stars appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明月開始發出光亮 並出現眾多繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:56.06,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How did it all end up here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這奇跡究竟如何產生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:03.47,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I am here at this crucial time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在關鍵時刻來到此處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:11.19,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hope I find what I came to find
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望我能找到我來找尋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:17.04,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm destined to be, the way I'm meant to be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這是註定好的 也是必須發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:23.08,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have to find my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我一定要找到我路
